column3: In celebration and calculation do we bring a Heavensturn gift, from the Far East to Eorzea. Long may we be of good blood!
Has <hex:020813E905FF07>m'lady<hex:FF07>m'lord<hex:03> perhaps misplaced the gift <hex:02080CE905FF04>she<hex:FF03>he<hex:03> was given, that which the giver and the gifted alike call the uma kabuto?
You are a <hex:02080FE905FF06>woman<hex:FF04>man<hex:03> fearless and clueless to lose an item of such import! I shall give you another, but misplace it not again.
